#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-sendlateragent; is an akonadi agent which allows you to send scheduled "
"mails once or repeatedly."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-sendlateragent; je posrednik akonadi, ki vam omogoča pošiljanje "
"načrtovane pošte enkrat ali večkrat."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &i18n-sendlateragent;"
msgstr "Uporaba &i18n-sendlateragent;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <menuchoice><guimenu>Message</guimenu><guimenuitem>Send Later</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> in &kmail;'s composer window to open a dialog "
"which allows you to schedule your emails to send at a specific date and time."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite <menuchoice><guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pošlji "
"pozneje</guimenuitem></menuchoice> v oknu za ustvarjanje &kmail;, da odprete "
"pogovorno okno, ki vam omogoča, da načrtujete pošiljanje svojih e-poštnih "
"sporočil na določen datum in čas."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&i18n-sendlateragent; Dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&i18n-sendlateragent; Pogovorno okno</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&i18n-sendlateragent; Dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&i18n-sendlateragent; Pogovorno okno</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>&i18n-sendlateragent; Dialog</para>"
msgstr "<para>&i18n-sendlateragent; Pogovorno okno</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Say you have constructed a brilliant email outlining tasks you wish your "
"employees to complete while you are at the conference, but you will be on an "
"airplane when you wish the email to be sent. Use this feature to send the "
"email at a precise date and time. To schedule the email to send later, first "
"check the <guilabel>Delay</guilabel> box and then select the date and time "
"on the <guilabel>Send at:</guilabel> menu."
msgstr ""
"Recimo, da ste sestavili odlično e-poštno sporočilo, v katerem so opisane "
"naloge, za katere želite, da jih vaši zaposleni opravijo, medtem ko ste na "
"konferenci, vendar boste na letalu, ko boste želeli, da se e-poštno "
"sporočilo pošlje. Uporabite to funkcijo za pošiljanje e-pošte ob natančnem "
"datumu in uri. Če želite načrtovati pošiljanje e-pošte pozneje, najprej "
"označite polje <guilabel>Zakasnitev</guilabel> in nato izberite datum in uro "
"v meniju <guilabel>Pošlji na:</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you need to send a weekly reminder email to your employees, you can "
"configure it to repeat sending the message by checking <guilabel>Repeat "
"every</guilabel> checkbox and selecting the desired intervals."
msgstr ""
"Če morate svojim zaposlenim poslati tedenski e-poštni opomnik, ga lahko "
"konfigurirate za ponavljajoče se pošiljanje sporočila, tako da potrdite "
"polje <guilabel>Ponovi vsak</guilabel> in izberete želene intervale."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can put the message in your queued messages by selecting the "
"<guibutton>Send Later</guibutton> button to schedule the message immediately."
msgstr ""
"Sporočilo lahko postavite med sporočila v čakalni vrsti tako, da izberete "
"gumb <guibutton>Pošlji pozneje</guibutton>, da takoj razporedite sporočilo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This agent works independent from &kmail; and does not need a running "
"&kmail; instance or &kmail; being in online mode to send scheduled emails."
msgstr ""
"Ta agent deluje neodvisno od &kmail; in ne potrebuje delujočega &kmail; "
"primerek ali &kmail; v spletnem načinu za pošiljanje načrtovanih e-poštnih "
"sporočil."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have no network connection when a scheduled message should be sent, "
"the agent will report an error and ask if you want to resend it later."
msgstr ""
"Če nimate omrežne povezave, ko bi moralo biti poslano načrtovano sporočilo, "
"bo posrednik sporočil napako in vas vprašal, ali ga želite znova poslati "
"pozneje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At login to a &kde; session the agent checks the scheduled messages and "
"sends all messages overdue since the last logout if necessary."
msgstr ""
"Ob prijavi v &kde; seji agent preveri načrtovana sporočila in po potrebi "
"pošlje vsa sporočila, ki so zapadla od zadnje odjave."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To change the options for emails you have scheduled to send later, use "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure &kmail;...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> then select the <guilabel>Plugins</guilabel> page "
"in &kmail; and press the configuration button against the <guilabel>Send "
"Later Agent</guilabel> item."
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti možnosti za e-pošto, ki ste jo načrtovali za pošiljanje "
"pozneje, uporabite <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj &kmail;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> nato "
"izberite <guilabel>Vtičniki</guilabel> strani v &kmail; in pritisnite gumb "
"za konfiguracijo proti elementu <guilabel>Pošlji agenta pozneje</guilabel>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Configure &i18n-sendlateragent;</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Konfigurirajte &i18n-sendlateragent;</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Configure &i18n-sendlateragent;</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Konfigurirajte &i18n-sendlateragent;</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Configure &i18n-sendlateragent;</para>"
msgstr "<para>Konfigurirajte &i18n-sendlateragent;</para>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This brings up a dialog that allows you to modify the schedule and remove "
"emails that have been sent using the send later feature."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže se pogovorno okno, ki vam omogoča spreminjanje urnika in "
"odstranjevanje e-poštnih sporočil, ki so bila poslana s funkcijo pošiljanja "
"pozneje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is not possible to change the content (body, headers &etc;) of a "
"scheduled message."
msgstr ""
"Vsebine (telesa, glave &etc;) načrtovanega sporočila ni mogoče spremeniti."

